# Per-directory Cloudflare account for `wrangler deploy` in this folder.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (gitignored) and paste an API token scoped to the
# SAME account as wrangler.toml's `account_id` (the Growhub account that owns
# growhub.com.hk / Email Routing / the Pages project).
#
# Create the token at:
#   Cloudflare Dashboard → My Profile → API Tokens → Create Token
#   → template "Edit Cloudflare Workers"  (or a custom token with
#      Account · Workers Scripts : Edit  for the Growhub account)
#
# wrangler (v3.60+/v4) auto-loads `.env` from the working directory, so running
#   cd worker/mailer && npx wrangler deploy
# will authenticate with THIS token and deploy to THIS account_id — regardless
# of which account `wrangler login` is signed into. That is the per-directory
# account switch: each project folder pins its own account_id + token.

CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=
